---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---
<DocsLayout title="Roadmap">
  <h1>Roadmap</h1>
  <p>
    This roadmap tracks planned features and improvements for EncodeSwarmr. All 8 phases are complete.
  </p>

  <h2>Phase 1 — UI Completeness ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Audio conversion page</li>
    <li>✅ Path mappings admin page</li>
    <li>✅ Agent enrollment tokens admin page</li>
    <li>✅ VNC "Open Remote Desktop" button</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 2 — Hardening ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ SHA-256 verification for agent self-upgrade</li>
    <li>✅ Agent upgrade rollback</li>
    <li>✅ OIDC end-to-end tests</li>
    <li>✅ Job expansion rollback</li>
    <li>✅ Offline journal cleanup</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 3 — Chunked Encoding UI ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Scene-based chunking config</li>
    <li>✅ Chunk boundary visualization</li>
    <li>✅ Merge/concat task generation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 4 — Observability &amp; Polish ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Agent resource utilization graphs</li>
    <li>✅ Structured audit logging</li>
    <li>✅ Bulk operations</li>
    <li>✅ Dark mode toggle</li>
    <li>✅ Capacity planning docs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 5 — Advanced Features ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Multi-controller HA</li>
    <li>✅ Cloud storage</li>
    <li>✅ Job scheduling/cron</li>
    <li>✅ OpenAPI 3.1 spec + SDKs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 6 — Production Readiness ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Security headers</li>
    <li>✅ API key auth</li>
    <li>✅ OIDC role mapping</li>
    <li>✅ Per-user notifications</li>
    <li>✅ Auto retry</li>
    <li>✅ Agent push upgrade</li>
    <li>✅ Log retention</li>
    <li>✅ Prometheus metrics</li>
    <li>✅ Grafana dashboards</li>
    <li>✅ Plugin system</li>
    <li>✅ Encoding presets</li>
    <li>✅ Cost estimation</li>
    <li>✅ Dashboard improvements</li>
    <li>✅ Job-from-template</li>
    <li>✅ Mobile-responsive UI</li>
    <li>✅ ADRs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 7 — Workflow &amp; Operations ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Email notifications</li>
    <li>✅ Per-user preferences</li>
    <li>✅ Auto-scaling hooks</li>
    <li>✅ Job chaining</li>
    <li>✅ Analysis→encode→audio→merge wizard</li>
    <li>✅ 13 audio codecs</li>
    <li>✅ Batch import</li>
    <li>✅ Output validation</li>
    <li>✅ Template dry-run</li>
    <li>✅ Intelligent retry</li>
    <li>✅ Job history archival + export</li>
    <li>✅ 12 audio presets</li>
    <li>✅ Output comparison view</li>
    <li>✅ ETA refinement</li>
    <li>✅ Template versioning</li>
    <li>✅ Adaptive chunking</li>
    <li>✅ Job preemption</li>
    <li>✅ Flow execution</li>
    <li>✅ Cost estimation learning</li>
    <li>✅ OpenTelemetry tracing</li>
    <li>✅ Kubernetes Helm</li>
    <li>✅ Visual flow pipeline editor (35 nodes)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Phase 8 — Professional Workflow ✅</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Watch folders (analysis-only, auto-detect new files)</li>
    <li>✅ Encoding rules engine (auto-suggest templates based on source properties)</li>
    <li>✅ Real-time WebSocket task log streaming</li>
    <li>✅ Two-pass encoding (flow node)</li>
    <li>✅ VMAF target encoding (flow node, iterative CRF binary search)</li>
    <li>✅ Agent pools / groups (named tag groups with UI management)</li>
    <li>✅ Queue management (pause/resume, drag-and-drop priority reordering)</li>
    <li>✅ Subtitle handling (extract/convert/embed/burn-in flow nodes)</li>
    <li>✅ Source preview thumbnails (auto-generated after analysis)</li>
    <li>✅ File manager (browse, move, delete, download from NAS)</li>
    <li>✅ Notification channels (Telegram, Pushover, ntfy)</li>
    <li>✅ Agent health deep-dive page (GPU temp, VRAM, disk, encoding stats)</li>
    <li>✅ Encoding profiles (template + audio + output bundled as one selection)</li>
    <li>✅ Agent update channels (stable/beta/nightly)</li>
    <li>✅ Audit log export + GDPR compliance</li>
    <li>✅ Session management (view/terminate active sessions)</li>
    <li>✅ Per-API-key rate limiting</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
